<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<Defs>
  <ThingDef Name="ThingBaseNinetailFox" ParentName="AnimalThingBase" Abstract="True">
    <description>The result of some scientist's obsession, this horse-sized fox is a marvelous exemplar of genetic engineering so advanced that it is indistinguishable from magic. They possess nine fiery orange tails, fiery breath, and fiery spirit. They are highly intelligent, and befriending one won't be too challenging, though quite risky - approaching one when it is in a bad mood is a fair way to go down in flames. Literally. Their reproduction is a big mystery. Some suspect energetic bead, but it is not confirmed.</description>
    <statBases>
		<Mass>50</Mass>
		<MoveSpeed>7.48</MoveSpeed>
		<ImmunityGainSpeed>1.5</ImmunityGainSpeed>
		<ToxicSensitivity>0.25</ToxicSensitivity>
		<ComfyTemperatureMin>-75</ComfyTemperatureMin>
		<ComfyTemperatureMax>40</ComfyTemperatureMax>
		<ArmorRating_Blunt>0.45</ArmorRating_Blunt>
		<ArmorRating_Sharp>0.65</ArmorRating_Sharp>
		<ArmorRating_Heat>1.0</ArmorRating_Heat>
